    I'd like to add a block where I offer an extra strap at a discount if you buy a watch here., Instead of add to cart. Create a button that says "Select Strap" that opens a popup where you can select a strap from a collection (that I can chose).

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

